headline: GE Aerospace gains after MS starts stock at OW on aftermarket demand
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley initiated coverage of GE Aerospace with an Overweight rating and a $425 price target, saying the market underestimates the its long term free cash flow and pricing power. Shares of the jet engine maker gained 1.5% in Friday premarket trading.
